oh my fucking jesus i can't believe i'm posting on here. i abandoned you livejournal and i am sorry for that. i do hope that you can forgive me. one of these days i'm going to try one of those fancy voice posting things like jew does. hey there fancy pants wow i really miss livejournal, myspace has taken over. i wouldn't be suprised if george pussy bush himself had one. you know it's bad when you go to see a movie and at the end of a preview it lists the myspace website for the movie. jesusgod this society is built around these damn machines. i wonder how fucked we would all be if we woke up tomorrow and there were no computers. that would be some funny stuff to see. i wonder how many people would commit suicide. anyways as you can all tell there is no real rhyme or reason to this post. i just missed my good ol el jay and wanted to stop in and say shalom.

Hey guys as you all know Katrina proved to be one angry bitch. I just wanted to let everyone know that if you wanted to help by donating items for the victims of Katrina they are doing a drive at the mall. It is being held tomorrow from 9-5 and is sponsored by Oldies 97.1. They are accepting all monetary donations as well as canned food, baby food, diapers, bottled water, toothbrushes, toothpaste, shampoo and conditioner, etc. If you don't think that you will be able to help out on such short notice the Red Cross is doing drives everywhere. You can visit www.redcross.org for more information. I hope that all of you will find it in yourself to help out. Thanks.
~V~
